summary:
Energetic conservationist and educational professional. 
* 3 years of working experience in various (research) projects in Europe, Africa and Latin America in the field of nature conservation, (nature) education and sustainable development;
* Experience in working with NGOs, governments and private organizations;
* Ability to work within a multi-cultural (research) team and with diverse stakeholders; 
* Over 5 years of experience in education as an education coordinator, accreditation professional, advisor, teacher and education assistant; 
* Supervised and supported large groups of (high-school/university) students, interns, trainees, volunteers and tourists; 
* Accredited 10 bachelors and masters according to the quality standards of the Dutch higher education system. 
* Personal interest in protecting our forests.
